description: If a modern take on traditional BBQ is what you've been craving, then Madera Smokehouse is the food truck for you.Going beyond the everyday ribs and pulled pork, Madera is creating some unique takes on what BBQ means. Cheese Fries, Smoked Sausages, and Tamale Waffles are just the start of the unforgettable experience you'll find here.Try something new, try something tasty, try something terrific today, with the help of your new friends at Madera Smokehouse!
name: Madera Smokehouse
